[size=6][b][color=#00ff00]Dungeon Optimizer[/color][/b][/size]
[i]Find the most efficient Mythic+ dungeon to run for your entire group.[/i]

[hr]

[size=5][color=#f8b700]What does it do?[/color][/size]

Dungeon Optimizer scans the gear of every member in your group, compares it against the [b]Best-in-Slot lists from Icy Veins[/b] for each player's class and spec, then [b]ranks every Mythic+ dungeon[/b] by how many BIS upgrades your group can get from it.

Stop wasting keys on dungeons that drop nothing useful. Run the one that matters.

[hr]

[size=5][color=#f8b700]Features[/color][/size]

[list]
[*] [b][color=#69ccf0]Full Group Scan[/color][/b] — Inspects equipped gear and specialization for every party/raid member automatically.
[*] [b][color=#69ccf0]3 BIS Modes[/color][/b] — Switch between [b]Overall[/b], [b]Mythic+[/b], and [b]Raid[/b] BIS lists depending on what your group is optimizing for.
[*] [b][color=#69ccf0]Smart Dungeon Ranking[/color][/b] — Each dungeon receives a score based on the total number of BIS upgrades available to the entire group. The best dungeon to run is always on top.
[*] [b][color=#69ccf0]Dungeon Exclusion[/color][/b] — Already ran Magister's Terrace this week? Check the box and it disappears from the ranking. No more duplicate runs.
[*] [b][color=#69ccf0]Per-Player Breakdown[/color][/b] — See exactly which player needs which item from which dungeon, with slot names and item names.
[*] [b][color=#69ccf0]Group Progress Summary[/color][/b] — At a glance, see each member's BIS completion percentage with class-colored names.
[*] [b][color=#69ccf0]Minimap Button[/color][/b] — Left-click to open, right-click to scan. Clean and simple.
[/list]

