[hr]

[size=5][color=#f8b700]How to Use[/color][/size]

[size=4][b]Step 1 — Open[/b][/size]
Type [b]/dopt[/b] or click the minimap button.

[size=4][b]Step 2 — Scan[/b][/size]
Click [b]"Scanner le groupe"[/b] or right-click the minimap button. The addon inspects every group member's gear and spec.

[size=4][b]Step 3 — Choose your mode[/b][/size]
Use the [b]Mode BIS[/b] dropdown to select:
[list]
[*] [b]Mythique+[/b] — BIS from dungeon drops only (default)
[*] [b]Overall[/b] — Best items from all sources combined
[*] [b]Raid[/b] — BIS from raid drops only
[/list]

[size=4][b]Step 4 — Exclude completed dungeons[/b][/size]
Check the boxes for dungeons your group has already run this week. They are removed from the ranking.

[size=4][b]Step 5 — Run the #1 dungeon[/b][/size]
The dungeon at the top of the list has the most BIS upgrades available for your group. Go run it.

[hr]

[size=5][color=#f8b700]Slash Commands[/color][/size]

[code]
/dopt          — Toggle the main window
/dopt scan     — Scan the group
/dopt reset    — Reset all dungeon exclusions
/dopt help     — Show help
[/code]

